articles.author: Nicholas Levine
articles.title: San Diego State: basketball's best-kept secret makes Final Four debut - The Guardian
articles.description: Brian Dutcher helped build one of college basketball’s strongest cultures at a program that once ranked among Division I’s worst. Now it’s paid off with the first Final Four in school history
